xt-lg\">Number pad</h2>\n                  <p className=\"panel-sub\">Enter recent past / upcoming i
njection date.</p>\n                </header>\n                <NumberPad\n                  onDigit
={onDigit}\n                  onClear={onClear}\n                  onBackspace={() => setDigitBuffer
